===Etymology===
From Greek ''[[sphairos]]'' ball.

===Noun===
'''sphere''' (''plural'' '''spheres''')

#A three-dimensional object every [[cross-section]] of which is a [[circle]].
#(''Mathematics'') The set:<math> \{x \in R^3|\,\, |x|=r \}; r \in R^+</math>
#The region in which something or someone is active.

